CapitaMall May Explore ION Purchase ‘When Time Is Right’

-- B y   C h i e n   M i   W o n g   a n d   Y u d i t h   H o
-- 
2011-07-19T12:00:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/capitamall-may-explore-purchase-of-ion-mall-ceo-says-correct-.html
CapitaMall Trust (CT) , Singapore’s
biggest retail property trust, may explore the purchase of the
ION shopping mall from its parent company “when the time is
right,” Simon Ho, chief executive officer of the trust’s
management company, told reporters today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
